Subject: Alex's SAM reports... (Mac)

With regard to Alex Zavatone's questions about SAM and WDEF, I would like to
report the following.

The WDEF in question was not a virus, but the standard system WDEF in a desktop
file. SAM reports this not as a WDEF infection, but rather as a code resource
of type WDEF in the desktop file, which might be an infection. There is no
cause for alarm in this instance.

